data.description: This 2 bedroom, 2 bath 1st floor condo in Summerlin Woods is being offered partially furnished so come and bring your finishing touches. You'll notice the southern exposure brings in light and warmth to this condo. The kitchen has ample counter space and cabinets, and open floor concept makes for easy living and entertaining. The primary bedroom has an en-suite bath and walk-in closet, and the guest bedroom offers privacy for family and guests. Enjoy the screened-in lanai overlooking the landscaped preserve. Amenities include shuffleboard, a sparkling pool, tennis courts, and car wash area. Summerlin Woods is a gated condo community with picturesque grounds and is within a close distance to Lakes Park, shopping, dining, beaches and the SWFL International Airport. Don't miss this opportunity!
